            <lg xml:id="TK673">
<l>ollumvā yellām viṉainaṉṟē yollākkāṟ </l>
<l> cellumvāy nōkkic ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Whenever it is possible (to overcome your enemy) the act (of fighting) is certainly good; if not, endeavour to employ some more successful method</l>
            </lg>
